00:11:49.260 --> 00:11:51.260
Papan buletin Thom Yorke dan LEGO Thom Yorke.

00:11:51.260 --> 00:11:54.260
Banyak saluran YouTube mengunggah video-video yang sangat menarik.

00:11:54.260 --> 00:11:57.260
